{
  "id": "RAW_d2c4fe7f",
  "title": "土耳其人有点“疯”，又把轻度游戏干到了千万美元月流水",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3NTQ4NjczNw==&mid=2650676495&idx=1&sn=486e61126207a6b75744aad0c7b242c5",
  "date": "2026-01-08 13:31:00",
  "author": "白鲸出海",
  "siteName": "白鲸出海",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"5 2 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 4px;border-color: rgb(53, 175, 253);min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5712890625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibJzB4CZdSVWAKCibu2odFyvhwzfIjF3T0MGSAp3aTtqic3DHpTDDicfNia9nmfd0YICFtXcrzZVhicMBaoicRKCapuicA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"555\" data-cropsely2=\"261\" data-imgfileid=\"503192825\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2e64dbfa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVWAKCibu2odFyvhwzfIjF3T0MGSAp3aTtqic3DHpTDDicfNia9nmfd0YICFtXcrzZVhicMBaoicRKCapuicA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">休闲游戏，已经被土耳其人走出了一条新路。</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: right;justify-content: flex-end;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: -1px 0px 10px;transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px 1px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(134, 147, 155);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">封面图片由AI生成</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">出品</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: right;margin-bottom: 8px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;3 2 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">｜白鲸出海编辑部</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">作者</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">｜孙京雷</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">混休跑出百万美元月流水，在一年前可能还算不错的成绩，但疯狂的土耳其人，在近一年里逐渐拉高标准。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如果说 Rollic 的「Color Block Jam」算是特殊案例，但最近 Loom Games 旗下「Pixel Flow」的月流水在上线后不久就迅速突破千万美元，预示着混休赛道的潜力可能远超此前的预测。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"padding:0px;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;vertical-align:bottom;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;width:614px !important;margin-top:0px;height:auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"503183761\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=156887aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVZ7JnPtEEqnkicw1JmIUibze4kI4o76tr2zVE3LC8g6wTX3sBXRJLOJP3ick53GT05KzcjvVROmLoJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">高下载推动流水上涨，</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">背后厂商已经在“精细化运作”</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0852641334569046\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1079\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503192831\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4c2f2805&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVWAKCibu2odFyvhwzfIjF3T0Y9ovEnOz152YE5SmpTI1bxtcQBtCm2QQH2bDJwiaAicy4bpVunBxF1iag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">Pixel Flow」（左图 2） 相比此前性质</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; line-height: 1em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">类似</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; line-height: 1em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">的</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">混休竞品（左图 1）增加了传送带机制，</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">在丰富视觉效果的同时增加了屏幕</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; line-height: 1em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">上半部分</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; line-height: 1em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">解谜</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">内容的深度，是最大的创新 | 图片来源：Pixel Flow</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不久前我们曾拆解过「Pixel Flow」的玩法。这款游戏的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">最大特点就是继承 Rollic 目前正在尝试的将屏幕一分为二或一分为三，再分别搭配休闲玩法，组合出新体验的机制；在这个基础上，「Pixel Flow」还在屏幕上方添加了“像素射击”以及“传送带”的设计，在提供益智玩法体验的同时，还强化了视觉快感，上线不久不错的吸量表现和商业化成绩，引得大量越南和国内厂商模仿</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（ 详见文章《</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3NTQ4NjczNw==&amp;mid=2650674842&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=726a61336b41249c07a2c91e41d07016&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"消除又上创新玩法，上线 70 天月流水有望突破百万美元\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">消除又上创新玩法，上线 70 天月流水有望突破百万美元</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">》）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.390625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503192830\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=deb998a5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVWAKCibu2odFyvhwzfIjF3T04veggURatAPFdMgZL6ypdJuPeVqBFibtLibSLSCcibmibyBonwfHSXK3WQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">「Pixel Flow」（ 蓝色 ） 已经在 2025 年 12 月</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">超过「Color Block Jam」（ 橙色 ），成为月流水</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">最高的混休游戏 | 数据来源：点点数据</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">虽然在当时看好「Pixel Flow」的发展前景，但其后续的增长速度依然让人震惊。data.ai 显示「Pixel Flow」最早在 2025 年 8 月上线，点点数据显示游戏 10 月才产生流水，但在 12 月的流水就已经高达 868 万美元，超过 Rollic 的「Color Block Jam」成为月流水最高的混休游戏。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Sensor Tower 更是显示游戏在 12 月的流水已经高达 1100 万美元 （约合 7692 万人民币）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不仅如此，「Pixel Flow」的日流水还在快速增长中，点点数据显示截止到 1 月 5 日已经达到 35 万美元左右；更有自媒体表示日流水已经超过百万美元，也就是一个月 3000 万美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.390625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503192832\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=af85a54c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVWAKCibu2odFyvhwzfIjF3T0fvPrngDPdzqAfv2w7prZx9vCEDDCvj7BvbODzWXXpmpJgJibdn4ToIw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">「Pixel Flow」的下载量也在 2025 年 10-12 月</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">期间明显增长，在 11 月已经超过</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">「Color Block Jam」 | 数据来源：点点数据</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">进一步观察可以发现，「Pixel Flow」的流水增长和下载量增长有直接关系。点点数据显示游戏下载量从 10 月的 103 万次迅速增长到了 12 月的 500 万次，增长近 4 倍。广大大数据显示，游戏在收入更高的 iOS 端广告投放力度也从 11 月中旬开始逐渐加大，目前每日投放素材数量依然在 120 条以上。不过相比「Color Block Jam」同期至少每天 200 条的素材而言并不算太高。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.35390625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503192833\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4e636eb2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVWAKCibu2odFyvhwzfIjF3T0sYrt7CgBS4liaMU3KDfrqlBS9TmfloX1ic8v71XiaPOj1eCSfNBiapyricw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">「Pixel Flow」的投放力度从 2025 年 11 月</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; line-height: 1em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">中旬</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">开始增加，目前依然处于高位 | 数据来源：广大大</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">用更少的素材量撬动更大的下载，观察可发现「Pixel Flow」的素材策略的确在 AI 的支持下有了一定调整。由于玩法本身趣味和观赏性都很强，所以上一次（10 月）我们观察的时候素材还是以直接展示玩法为主；但进入到投放力度最强的 12 月，一批新投放素材会在片头率先展示游戏虚拟形象“方块射手小猪”的动画，然后再开始展示玩法，充分调动玩家兴趣。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">从 12 月开始，「Pixel Flow」投放的许多视频</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">素材都会率先展示一段和“方块小猪”相关的动画，</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">然后再演示玩法 | 视频来源：Pixel Flow</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这些动画有的是小猪在坐着传送带（游戏里的另一个标志性物品）玩耍，有的是聚在一起发射炮弹打闹，但相同的一点就是它们都极有可能都由 AI 生成，甚至一些素材上还依然打着 Veo 等视频生成模型的 Logo。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">从这些操作明显可以看出，土耳其厂商长于游戏玩法创新，但较轻的游戏机制很难抵挡抄袭，希望通过强化 IP 形象的操作来加强用户的粘性，这个方法已经被以色列厂商 Superplay 验证。另一个有意思的点是，上面展示的高曝光素材竟然长达 58s，结束卡片搭配试玩广告，厂商在有意识地筛选玩家。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8943850267379679\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"748\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503192834\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b2849257&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVWAKCibu2odFyvhwzfIjF3T0eNBxb5K7VZJjKOvmZdoWvENWSZ4k5EspkMbibc4LZO0lsVYzOMZ23Lg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">“小猪”们在「Pixel Flow」的 AIGC 素材里</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">存在感不断上升，很可能是 Loom Games&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">今后试图 IP 化运营的预兆 | 图片来源：广大大</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:32px 8px 8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-wid