xt-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">看似年轻的“萌新”团队，</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">背后是第一批做出大流水产品的混休大佬</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5630914826498423\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1268\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503192835\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2ded6616&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVWAKCibu2odFyvhwzfIjF3T0vFpSG99vHkpj6xtvMMuQd6hQt0BKXdzeGDyhkVbxvWNybbwJLR59mg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">Loom Games 联合创始人 Kübra Gündoğan</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; line-height: 1em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">（左）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">和 Emre Çelik 都已经拥有丰富的混休</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">产品研发经验 | 图片来源：Gamigion</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对玩法进行创新，搭配拥抱 AIGC 素材的营销策略，让「Pixel Flow」在仅仅 3 个月内成长为了混休 Top 1。而不同于「Color Block Jam」背后是超休时期就已经颇具规模的大厂 Rollic，「Pixel Flow」的发行厂商 Loom Games 在 2025 年 7 月才成立（领英资料），最近甚至还吸引了头部休闲厂商 Tripledot 创始人 Akın Babayiğit 领导的种子轮投资。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6096938775510204\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1176\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503192836\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=221a5e79&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVWAKCibu2odFyvhwzfIjF3T0tkEGgBoZiaXGskpo8kqRgT5iamE0sLznnAhg0fKHYQN2SjnbBMww7Gdg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4167424931756142\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1099\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503192837\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3acab530&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVWAKCibu2odFyvhwzfIjF3T0PEhGAVbkd1afeJsDN4NQY6Vco9ViapHDdyrskSUJtvyOGIOccKsL8dA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">Loom Games 的两位创始人此前是另一家</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">小厂商 Crescive Games 的创始人（上图），</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">Crescive Games 开发过最著名的产品就是由&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">Rollic 发行的解绳题材混休游戏「Twisted Tangle」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">（下图） | 图片来源：LinkedIn、Crescive Games</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">仔细调查后我们才得知，表面看上去完全是个新团队的 Loom Games，背后其实是最早做出大流水的混休产品之一「Twisted Tangle」的主创。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">两位创始人此前已经成立了另一家小厂 Crescive Games，最出名的产品是交给 Rollic 发行的「Twisted Tangle」。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过将超休游戏常见的解绳玩法和消除体验搭上关系，「Twisted Tangle」在 2 年前迅速走红，成为第一批月流水过百万美元的混休产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更值得注意的是，由于这类游戏更多在于玩法创新，投放素材也是玩法带动流量，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Loom Games 的成功很可能会给今后与 Rollic 合作的众多中小团队以启发，从此前“自己开发游戏、交给 Rollic 发行”的合作框架里走出来，尝试自主研发发行的新路线。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前市场上已经出现了不少月流水接近或超过 100 万美元的土耳其中小团队，这些厂商里很有可能就会有下一个 Loom Games。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:32px 8px 8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"padding:0px;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;vertical-align:bottom;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;width:614px !important;margin-top:0px;height:auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"503183761\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=156887aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVZ7JnPtEEqnkicw1JmIUibze4kI4o76tr2zVE3LC8g6wTX3sBXRJLOJP3ick53GT05KzcjvVROmLoJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic\"></span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">重内容 vs 重玩法，越来越赚钱的</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">休闲游戏，分化出明显的 2 条路径</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此前，由于以柠檬微趣和点点互动为代表的出海厂商在 Merge 和消除赛道实现了突破性发展，再加上许多以短剧起家的厂商开始入局，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">不少业内人士认为休闲游戏的未来很可能是在已经成熟的 Merge 和消除基础上做内容填充与优化，让玩家不止是在玩游戏，更在“追剧情”。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这类的新玩家有之前选题《</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3NTQ4NjczNw==&amp;mid=2650675723&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1f952aeebcda28d1031d9d6142d4bd88&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"时隔很久，终于又有出海消除登上美国 iOS 游戏总榜\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">时隔很久，终于又有出海消除登上美国 iOS 游戏总榜</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">》的厂商。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">相比之下，这 2年的混合休闲其实也是在做“消除”的变体，但完全在走另一条路，注重玩法创新、数值调控以及内购设计优化的“玩法消耗型”产品</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，出海厂商在这条路线上的进展就相对慢很多。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">由于这一赛道本身发展历史也远远比 Merge 和消除更短，所以头部产品的成绩也相对还不那么突出。但随着最近一年「Color Block Jam」、「Screwdom」以及「Pixel Flow」等产品的不断涌现，混合休闲的潜力也在不断得到证明。但如上文所述，“重玩法”产品防御门槛低，很容易被模仿。目前「Pixel Flow」已经在市场上出现了多款同类竞品，也有不少跑出了成绩。下一个选题，我们会对此进行盘点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">参考文章：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">Pixel Flow Raises Seed Round Led by Akın Babayiğit and e2vc | Gamigion</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">链接：<a href=\"https://www.gamigion.com/pixel-flow-raises-seed-round-led-by-akin-babayigit-and-e2vc/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gamigion.com/pixel-flow-raises-seed-round-led-by-akin-babayigit-and-e2vc/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);\">数据来自SimilarWeb、点点数据、Semrush、广大大等三方平台，可能与真实数据中存在一定误差，仅供参考。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文分析了土耳其厂商 Loom Games 如何凭借《Pixel Flow》的玩法创新和 AIGC 营销，实现轻度游戏千万级月流水，并揭示了休闲游戏市场“重内容”与“重玩法”两条发展路径。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文分析了土耳其厂商 Loom Games 如何凭借《Pixel Flow》的玩法创新和 AIGC 营销，实现轻度游戏千万级月流水，并揭示了休闲游戏市场“重内容”与“重玩法”两条发展路径。",
  "summary": "本文深度剖析了土耳其轻度游戏厂商如何通过创新玩法和 AIGC 营销策略，将混合休闲游戏推向千万美元月流水。文章以 Loom Games 开发的《Pixel Flow》为例，详细分析了其玩法创新点（如分屏玩法、像素射击、传送带机制），以及如何通过引入 AI 生成动画素材强化 IP 形象，实现低成本高效率的买量增长。文章进一步揭示了 Loom Games 创始人团队的深厚背景，他们曾是另一款成功混休游戏《Twisted Tangle》的主创，这反映出土耳其厂商在轻度游戏领域的深厚积累和快速迭代能力。最后，文章探讨了休闲游戏市场正在分化成“重内容”和“重玩法”两条路线，并指出玩法创新型产品虽然容易被模仿，但其潜力巨大，呼吁出海厂商关注并学习这类创新模式。",
